+### 4.6 Trusted CA / TLS trust baseline
+
+Document pre-feature behavior for platform and enterprise CA:
+
+- **Platform CA:** CNO-injected `external-secrets-trusted-ca-bundle` ConfigMap; mount at `/etc/pki/tls/certs`; historically proxy-gated via `getProxyConfiguration`.
+- **Enterprise CA:** Absent on ESC `CommonConfigs` before feature; upstream `caProvider` on SecretStore CRDs is separate scope.
+- **Key files:** `pkg/controller/external_secrets/configmap.go`, `deployments.go`.
+- **CommonConfigs blast radius:** Fields on `CommonConfigs` regenerate both ESC and ESM CRDs.
